Rating: 3
While this pie filling is delicious, the accompanying pate brisee (dough) recipe makes an amount of dough insufficient for a 9" pie. It's very frustrating to try to roll dough out enough to fill the pan and cover the pie when there simply is not enough of it to do so. Other comparable dough recipes I have seen call for similar ingredients but an additional 3/4 cup of flour. Next time I try this recipe I'll use 2 cups of flour rather than the 1-1/4 called for.

